<subSubSection id="7D9F722908114B405FB37ABA804713A1" pageId="0" pageNumber="253" type="observations">
<paragraph id="DE119D99F4C4ACA227B8E5CD9F1BD0CA" pageId="0" pageNumber="253">Observations.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="51870F1CB4925813E4932AC83AF0CD70" pageId="0" pageNumber="253">
Due to the lowered status of 
<taxonomicName id="2660FA238F085FA31482C9B18BA5B0B0" authorityName="Lopes &amp; Carpenter &amp; Noll" authorityYear="2021" class="Insecta" family="Eumenidae" genus="Ctenochilus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Ctenochilus" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="253" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="902A5220B6D313466CF7F6FC5F7A5375" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="253">Ctenochilus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to subgenus, the species belonging to this group require new combinations. These are given in Suppl. material 3.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
